          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "With over 15 years industry experience,  Cliphair has become the UK’s leading Remy Human Hair extension supplier,[read-more] with hundreds of thousands of digital shoppers all over the world. From <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-hair-extensions\" title=\"Clip In collection page\">Clip Ins</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/tape-in-hair-extensions\" title=\"Tape In collection page\">Tape In Extensions</a> to <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/micro-ring-loop-hair-extensions\" title=\"Micro Ring hair extension collection page\">Permanent Micro Rings</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/one-piece-clip-in-hair-extensions\" title=\"One Piece hair extension collection page\">One Pieces</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-ponytail-extensions\" title=\"Ponytail collection page\">Ponytail Extensions</a>, we are without doubt the no. 1 premium hair extension seller on the market.If you’re new to wearing hair extensions and want to take the leap, you can learn everything you need to know about choosing and purchasing extensions in our <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/hair-extension-buying-guide-and-hair-glossary\" title=\"Cliphair: Hair Extension Buying Guide & Glossary\">Ultimate Buying Guide</a>. For application and maintenance advice, you can also read our <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-look-after-hair-extensions-ultimate-care-guide\" title=\"Cliphair Guides: How To Look After Hair Extensions\">Hair Extension Care Guide</a>.With a wide, stunning <a href=\"https://www.cliphair.co.uk/pages/hair-extensions-by-colour\" title=\"Hair Colour Chart\">range of shades</a>, our premium Remy Hair Extensions can be delivered straight to your door, 7 days a week – no matter where you are. Experience unmatched shine, volume and versatility with our 100% real human hair extensions made from the best quality Remy hair. Choose luxury with Cliphair!"
          }
        }
      },
